    "The attacker persistently bombards the host with spam requests until it becomes overwhelmed and ceases to function.",
    "Typically, DoS attacks are directed at data communication systems, of Abnormal Traffic, Encryption and Decryption Analysis, Network Segmentation Analysis, IoT Device Profiling, and Real-time Monitoring.",
    "• Data TheftData theft in IoT security refers to malicious actors' unauthorized acquisition, copying, or retrieval of sensitive or confidential data from IoT devices, networks, or systems.",
